page_0: "That fool Sturmdrang will get us all killed. He follows the chance whims of Mohana, no matter the costs. It's clear to the rest of the crew and me that Mohana forsook us long ago, if ever she favoured us at all. If we are to have a chance at retiring from this sinful life, we must wrest our fair share of the wealth from our faith-blinded Captain. Some have already expressed their doubts to me, but others may take some convincing. And there is also the problem of the power he wields."
